<div class="greeting">
  Hi {{firstName}},
</div>

<div class="alert alert-danger">
  <strong>⚠️ Payment Overdue</strong><br>
  Your rent payment is now overdue. Please make payment immediately to avoid additional late fees.
</div>

<div class="info-box">
  <h3>Overdue Payment Details</h3>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Amount Due:</span>
    <span class="info-value"><strong>KES {{amount}}</strong></span>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Original Due Date:</span>
    <span class="info-value">{{dueDate}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Days Overdue:</span>
    <span class="info-value"><strong>{{daysOverdue}} days</strong></span>
  </div>
  {{#if lateFee}}
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Late Fee:</span>
    <span class="info-value">KES {{lateFee}}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="info-row">
    <span class="info-label">Total Amount:</span>
    <span class="info-value"><strong>KES {{totalAmount}}</strong></span>
  </div>
  {{/if}}
</div>

<a href="{{paymentUrl}}" class="button">Pay Now</a>

<div class="message">
  <p><strong>Important:</strong> Continued non-payment may result in:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Additional late fees</li>
    <li>Negative impact on your rental history</li>
    <li>Legal action as per your lease agreement</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="message">
  <p>If you're experiencing financial difficulties, please contact us immediately to discuss payment arrangements.</p>
  <p><strong>Contact:</strong> 0700NYUMBA or <a href="mailto:support@nyumbasync.co.ke">support@nyumbasync.co.ke</a></p>
</div>
